OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist soon clearing then a
OL,6,Fdry day with long spells of sunshine.
OL,7,FBecoming very warm again in the west
OL,8,Fbut cooler towards the east coast.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA sunny evening for most but
OL,11,Fsome low cloud will affect the east
OL,12,Fcoast. Dry with clear spells overnight
OL,13,Fbut low cloud will feed inland over
OL,14,Fthe Lothians and Borders.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FEarly low cloud in east will
OL,17,Fmostly burn off but some will continue
OL,18,Fto afflict the coasts. Otherwise,
OL,19,Fanother dry day with plenty of
OL,20,Fsunshine. Becoming warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
