OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,6,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine.
OL,7,FWarm in the west with the best of the
OL,8,Fsunshine, cloudier and cooler at times
OL,9,Fin the east.
